liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Oh it needed something special from England to prise apart this barnacle of a partnership and it was delivered to them by Mark Wood and their former skipper at first slip. A stunning one-handed catch to his left, Bairstow again did not move to a catch that was probably his, but Root stuck the left hand out and took a brilliant grab. Labuschagne goes for 9 from 82 deliveries. England finally has its breakthrough.
